div.div: The wasp-packet-forwarder is responsible for processing incoming traffic form the LoRaWAN network. This service identifies a configured sensor, parses the sensor packet to a set of readings, matches the sensor to a configured asset, analyses the readings against a set of event generators for the asset and then forwards the analysed data. The data is forwarded to a PostgreSQL database and can be additionally processed by an email forwarder for alert events and an MQTT broker for reprocessing.
